{title: Keyboard Chord Definitions}

{define: Am keys 0 3 7}
{define: C keys 0 4 7}
{define: Dm keys 2 5 9}
{define: Em keys 4 7 11}
{define: F keys 5 9 0}
{define: G keys 7 11 2}
{define: Bdim keys 11 2 5}

{start_of_verse}
[Am]Playing on the [C]piano
[Dm]Fingers on the [Em]keys
[F]Melodies are [G]flowing
[Am]Gentle as the [Bdim]breeze
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]Ivory and [F]ebony
[G]Harmony in [Am]time
[C]Every chord a [F]memory
[G]Every note [C]divine
{end_of_chorus}
